author: ThePopularEagle
description: The Popular Eagle (TPE for short) is a long time Stormbound Youtuber, having created content and guides since as far back as 2018. TPE is also on Twitter and Discord.

author: Emkaem
description: Emkaem is a former member of Paladin Studios, the original company behind Stormbound and has been playing and creating content since the early days of the game.

author: The_mirc
description: The_mirc is an active and high-profile Stormbound player with a maxed out collection, active on Discord and contributing by composing new decks and trying new strategies.

author: RecklessRush
description: RecklessRush is a popular Stormbound community manager known for his eponymous deck which focuses on aggressive rush strategies.

author: Frostkhan
description: Frostkhan is a high-rank player producing a lot of Stormbound videos when they experiment with various decks and strategies, especially during Brawls.

author: LazyLotazo
description: LazyLotazo is a popular Stormbound Youtuber regularly creating new videos.

author: Stratarts
description: Stratarts is an avid Spanish gamer and active member of the community who mainly uploads brawl videos.

author: AlsterSkyreader
description: Alster Skyreader is a winter rush player who consistenty plays in the Heroes League and shares his matches on YouTube.

author: ThomasPetree
description: Playing since October 2018, Thomas Petree is a Stormbound veteran always looking for ways to get an edge in the game.
